# ============================================================
# Trivy ignore rules for bjjeire-terraform-azurerm-aks
# ============================================================
# Each entry suppresses a known false-positive or an accepted
# risk. Justifications are documented inline.
# ============================================================

# tls_private_key / RSA private key stored in Terraform state
# The SSH key-pair is generated here intentionally. The private
# key is immediately written to Azure Key Vault (kv_secret_values)
# and is never exposed outside of the deployment pipeline.
AVD-GEN-0001

# AKS: API server authorized IP ranges
# Configured by the module consumer via
# var.aks_api_server_authorized_ip_ranges. Trivy cannot resolve
# variable values at static-analysis time so it treats the field
# as unset. The caller is responsible for restricting access.
AVD-AZU-0041

# AKS: RBAC not enabled
# Controlled by var.aks_role_based_access_control_enabled.
# Trivy cannot resolve variable values at static-analysis time.
AVD-AZU-0040

# AKS: Network policy not configured
# Controlled by var.aks_network_policy. Trivy cannot resolve
# variable values at static-analysis time.
AVD-AZU-0042
